reviewText:
Oswald is super sweet, great for toddlers and preschoolers. Gentle, kind lessons, fun friends, great music, cute adventures. Features four episodes:
- Odd One Out
- Goodbye Best Friend
- Friends Indeed
- Sammy Starfish Live

This is one of the rare cartoons that you are still able to watch on Nick Jr. that is not loud or annoying. As the parent, I even enjoy it! I would highly recommend any tape or DVD of Oswald to a parent of a little one. Even my 9yr. old niece loves Oswald!
And this is one of my favorite cartoons, ever! It's well animated and just so sweet. I love it.
But well worth it, anyway.  We have gotten hours and hours of viewing from this tape!  Oswald is the best!
